Frankly, neither was I.

34
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:33,100
Charley was the star of the team. Charley

35
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,100
Yeah. Thanks.

36
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:36,100
Well, how're you been, Philip?

37
00:10:36,100 --> 00:10:39,100
Oh, working too hard.

38
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,100
Doesn't show.

39
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,100
How's Ellen? Ellen

40
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:43,100
Fine, thank you.

41
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:45,100
And how's Marge? Marge

42
