52
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:10,100
Well, thanks.

53
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:12,100
I'll wait outside.

54
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:14,100
Good luck, Son.

55
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:17,100
Did you bring your transcript from high school?

56
00:11:17,100 --> 00:11:18,100
Yes, sir.

57
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:19,100
Right here.

58
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:20,100
Thank you.

